docs {
  whole-API discovery: every endpoint + the dayz action allowlist (public, no auth)
  
  The one place to see the entire surface. `endpoints` is auto-collected from the live route table (new endpoints/namespaces appear here for free), and `actions.dayz` expands the single POST /dayz/:action route into its named actions. Per-namespace action detail also lives at GET /dayz/actions.
}
